# 4-to-2 Encoder Using Verilog

## Description
This project implements a **4-to-2 Encoder** using **Verilog HDL**. It includes the encoder design, testbench, and waveform generation for simulation.

## Features
- 4-to-2 Encoder
- Verilog HDL
- Testbench included
- GTKWave waveform support

## Tools Used
- Verilog HDL
- Icarus Verilog
- GTKWave
- VS Code

## Files
- `encoder4x2.v` – Encoder design
- `encoder4x2_tb.v` – Testbench
- `encoder4x2.vcd` – Waveform file

